  "raw_block": "–1. Also called JUDAH and JUDAEA\n–(The southern division of Palestine)\n  .It extended from the Jordan River and the Dead Sea to the Mediterranean \nSea, and from Shiloh on the north to the wilderness on the southMt 4:25;Lu 5:17;Joh 4:47,54\n  .The term applies to all of Palestine inLu 1:5\n  .It applies to the territory east of the Jordan River inMt 19:1;Mr 10:1;Lu 23:5\n–2. Wilderness of\n  .Called Beth-arabahJos 15:6,61\n  .Assigned to BenjaminJos 18:22\n  .John the Baptist preaches inMt 3:1;Lu 3:3",
